Summary: golden colored star flew though Vail last night, no flashing airplane lights on it.
divs: Sighting DetailsWe were outside the Plimpton's house, a house my friend Kyle takes care of for rich people living in Arizona. While he was trying to get the door locked I noticed a golden colored star flying about airplane speed, mentioned to him to take a look. He agreed that he had never seen anything of the sort before, neither had I. Object flew east to west, right over I70. Distance to the object was unknown.
